videos.description: TaQuon Marshall takes the snap and cuts across the field for a 28-yard Georgia Tech touchdown to tie Miami in the 1st quarter.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech QB takes it himself for 28-yard TD

videos.description: TaQuon Marshall runs a bootleg and takes it in for an 8-yard touchdown, his 2nd rushing score vs. Miami.

videos.headline: Miami RB takes it 22 yards to the house
